-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

Text Annotation
their-4:their
Lemma Annotation
their-4:they
POS
their-4:PRP$
NER
their-4:O



(ROOT (S (SBAR (IN As) (S (NP (NP (JJ different)) (PP (IN as) (NP (PRP$ their) (NNS backgrounds) (CC and) (NNS families)))) (VP (VBD were)))) (, ,) (NP (PRP it)) (VP (VBD was) (ADVP (DT no) (NN doubt)) (NP (NP (DT this) (NN strong-female)) (, ,) (NP (JJ weak-male) (NN similarity))) (SBAR (IN that) (S (NP (PRP he)) (VP (VBD had) (PP (IN in) (NP (NN mind))))))) (. .)))
-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)

      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

(ROOT (S (SBAR (IN As) (S (NP (NP (JJ different)) (PP (IN as) (NP (PRP$ their) (NNS backgrounds) (CC and) (NNS families)))) (VP (VBD were)))) (, ,) (NP (PRP it)) (VP (VBD was) (ADVP (DT no) (NN doubt)) (NP (NP (DT this) (NN strong-female)) (, ,) (NP (JJ weak-male) (NN similarity))) (SBAR (IN that) (S (NP (PRP he)) (VP (VBD had) (PP (IN in) (NP (NN mind))))))) (. .)))
-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)

  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)

(ROOT (S (SBAR (IN As) (S (NP (NP (JJ different)) (PP (IN as) (NP (PRP$ their) (NNS backgrounds) (CC and) (NNS families)))) (VP (VBD were)))) (, ,) (NP (PRP it)) (VP (VBD was) (ADVP (DT no) (NN doubt)) (NP (NP (DT this) (NN strong-female)) (, ,) (NP (JJ weak-male) (NN similarity))) (SBAR (IN that) (S (NP (PRP he)) (VP (VBD had) (PP (IN in) (NP (NN mind))))))) (. .)))
-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

(ROOT (S (SBAR (IN As) (S (NP (NP (JJ different)) (PP (IN as) (NP (PRP$ their) (NNS backgrounds) (CC and) (NNS families)))) (VP (VBD were)))) (, ,) (NP (PRP it)) (VP (VBD was) (ADVP (DT no) (NN doubt)) (NP (NP (DT this) (NN strong-female)) (, ,) (NP (JJ weak-male) (NN similarity))) (SBAR (IN that) (S (NP (PRP he)) (VP (VBD had) (PP (IN in) (NP (NN mind))))))) (. .)))
-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

(ROOT (S (SBAR (IN As) (S (NP (NP (JJ different)) (PP (IN as) (NP (PRP$ their) (NNS backgrounds) (CC and) (NNS families)))) (VP (VBD were)))) (, ,) (NP (PRP it)) (VP (VBD was) (ADVP (DT no) (NN doubt)) (NP (NP (DT this) (NN strong-female)) (, ,) (NP (JJ weak-male) (NN similarity))) (SBAR (IN that) (S (NP (PRP he)) (VP (VBD had) (PP (IN in) (NP (NN mind))))))) (. .)))
-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)
    -> that/IN (mark)
    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)

-> strong-female/NN (root)
  -> were/VBD (advcl)
    -> As/IN (mark)
    -> different/JJ (nsubj)
      -> backgrounds/NNS (nmod:as)
        -> as/IN (case)
        -> their/PRP$ (nmod:poss)
        -> and/CC (cc)
        -> families/NNS (conj:and)
      -> families/NNS (nmod:as)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> it/PRP (nsubj)
  -> was/VBD (cop)
  -> doubt/NN (advmod)
    -> no/DT (neg)
  -> this/DT (det)
  -> ,/, (punct)
  -> similarity/NN (appos)
    -> weak-male/JJ (amod)
  -> had/VBD (ccomp)

    -> he/PRP (nsubj)
    -> mind/NN (nmod:in)
      -> in/IN (case)
  -> ./. (punct)
